==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unresisted
<hw>Un`re*sist"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not resisted;
unopposed.</def> <rj><au>Bentley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Resistless; <as>as, <ex>unresisted</ex>
fate</as>.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unresistible</ent>⟦br⟧
